About Me
Hello! My name is Maram ZRIBI. I'm from Tunisia .I am studying software enginneering at the national engineering school of tunis (ENIT). During my time here, I gained valuable experience through various entry-level positions, which greatly enhanced my work ethic, communication skills, and adaptability.

My journey into the world of technology began with a strong passion for problem-solving, which led me to pursue the Computer Systems Technology program. Despite its challenges, I remained determined and forged lasting friendships that supported me throughout this demanding program. Throughout my studies at ENIT, I had the opportunity to engage in fascinating projects.
